    <text id="A1127T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Argenbright discusses a doctor appointment about whether he's fit for military
                    service.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1861-11-24">November 24<hi rend="super">th</hi> 1861</date>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Dear <orig reg="Sir">Sur</orig></salute>
                </opener>

                <p>i received your letter yesterday and was glad to hear from you and this day i
                    thought i <orig reg="would">wod</orig>
                    <orig reg="write">rite</orig> you <add hand="h1" place="inline">a</add> few
                    lines to let you <orig reg="know">no</orig> how i am well i tell you that i seen
                    the <orig reg="doctor">docktor</orig> today and i <orig reg="asked">axet</orig>
                    him if i was fit for <orig reg="Service">Survis</orig> and he told me he thought
                    not i told him where worked i was <orig reg="too">to</orig>
                    <orig reg="weak">week</orig> to <orig reg="have">half</orig> work and i am <orig
                        reg="nervous">nervis</orig> when i work and my flesh is soft and i <orig
                        reg="can't">cant</orig> Stand <orig reg="whole">hole</orig> and i am
                        <unclear>hild</unclear>
                    <orig reg="directly">directley</orig> but i <orig reg="tell">tel</orig> you i
                    will <orig reg="come">com</orig> on as Soon as i think any <orig reg="new"
                    >neu</orig> flesh can stand the cold <orig reg="though">thoe</orig> i think i
                    will try it in <orig reg="two">too</orig> or three weeks at most and <del
                        hand="h1">G</del> George Bayley Says he will <orig reg="come">com</orig>
                    with me the <orig reg="doctor">docktor</orig> Says he <orig reg="ain't"
                    >ant</orig> fit yet for <orig reg="Service">Survis</orig><pb n="2"/></p>
                <p>I had nothing much to <orig reg="write">rite</orig> to you but to <orig
                        reg="give">giv</orig> you <orig reg="some">som</orig> satisfaction of what i
                    had <orig reg="wrote">rote</orig> to you i will Send <orig reg="those"
                    >thoes</orig> few lines the <orig reg="doctor">docktor</orig>
                    <orig reg="give">giv</orig> to us <orig reg="today">to day</orig> I wish you
                        <orig reg="would">wod</orig>
                    <orig reg="write">rite</orig> to me in a few days and let me <orig reg="know"
                    >no</orig> if i <orig reg="could">cod</orig> get a <unclear>cag</unclear> from
                    Strasburg to the camp and if get it than i will <orig reg="give">giv</orig> you
                    yon long <unclear>dram</unclear>
                    <orig reg="Some">Som</orig> of old bills second best</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute/>
                    <signed>A. G. Argenbright</signed>
                    <seg type="postscript">
                        <name type="recipient">To <abbr expan="Captain">Cap</abbr> F. C.
                        Roberts</name>
                    </seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
